# IMPORTANT SECURITY NOTICE:
# This .gitignore protects sensitive information including:
# - Database connection strings (MongoDB Atlas credentials)
# - JWT secrets and API keys
# - Admin credentials and passwords
# - SSL certificates and private keys
# - User uploaded files and temporary data
#
# NEVER commit .env files or any files containing:
# - Passwords or authentication tokens
# - Database connection strings
# - API keys or secrets
# - SSL certificates or private keys
